Amethyst Crystal:
Amethyst crystal formation are part of the quartz family of crystals which is the most abundant mineral formation on the planet, is one of the most important gemstone in crystal healing, it's an excellent stone to improves visualization.
It's a stone of peace and helps bring LOVE AND HAPPINESS TO ALL.

Amethyst is one of the most powerful crystals you can find

Amethyst is a meditative and calming stone which works in the emotional and spiritual planes to provide calm, balance, patience, and peace.
It also is said to bring emotional stability and inner strength. This stability and strength not only helps one hold firm in one's life, but it can enhance flexibility and cooperation. To be flexible at need is a sure sign of strength

Amethyst is a crystal whose energy can be multi-faceted. It can be as gentle as a petal or as wild as a storm. Many seem to see it as always gentle and calming. It certainly can be. Amethyst is a type of quartz, though, full of all the energy and power of its parent stone. Don't hesitate to use Amethyst when great power is needed. It can bring in that energy with both force and balance
